      "3": "kai esontai autois ai poleis katoikein kai ta aforismata autwn estai tois kthnesin autwn kai pasi tois tetraposin autwn",
      "4": "kai ta sugkurounta twn polewn as dwsete tois leuitais apo teicous ths polews kai exw discilious phceis kuklw",
      "5": "kai metrhseis exw ths polews to klitos to pros anatolas discilious phceis kai to klitos to pros liba discilious phceis kai to klitos to pros qalassan discilious phceis kai to klitos to pros borran discilious phceis kai h polis meson toutou estai umin kai ta omora twn polewn",
