      "7": "pasas tas poleis dwsete tois leuitais tessarakonta kai oktw poleis tautas kai ta proasteia autwn",
      "8": "kai tas poleis as dwsete apo ths katascesews uiwn israhl apo twn ta polla polla kai apo twn elattonwn elattw ekastos kata thn klhronomian autou hn klhronomhsousin dwsousin apo twn polewn tois leuitais",
